The paper discusses the security of wireless air traffic communication systems, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and network security (cs.NI). The paper also discusses countermeasures and approaches for secure new technologies, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also examines the awareness and opinions of aviation experts, which falls under the category of human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and social and information networks (cs.SI).
